title: Figures On A Beach  -Discography with EP and Remixes -80's New W
description: Figures On A Beach (Alternative Synth, New Wave, Pop Rock), 1980's Group that started out well and played by some but not enough for others. Early EP and remixes need to be put in a Re-Issue. The EP includes early tracks (4) plus the big hit Breathless. other mixes are included as well. most of what they have should be in this so called Discography.  Hope you enjoy all these !! Feel free to add or remake this discography, if there is more (I did leave a few out and was rushed to get these out there) please add
